Numeric Expiry as TTL
    [Tags]  sanity  syncgateway  ttl
    [Documentation]
    ...  1. PUT /db/doc1 via SG with property "_exp":3
    ...     PUT /db/doc2 via SG with property "_exp":10
    ...  2. Wait five seconds
